description:
This is a 25 minute workout called '25 min FULL BODY STRETCH (No Talking - for Relaxation, Flexibility & Stress Relief)' from the channel MadFit.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching and Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This 25 min gentle stretching routine is perfect if you're looking to increase your flexibility, mobility, and relax. There is NO TALKING - just relaxing music and gentle audio cues to let you know when to switch positions.
